      • onNewMonth

        protected void onNewMonth()
        Description copied from class: OAMonthCalendar
        Called when a new month is being displayed. This is used when working with objectCache, so that objects can be loaded from datasource that match the selected date range for the new month.
        Overrides:
        onNewMonth in class OAMonthCalendar
